X-Windows: A moment of convenience, a lifetime of regret.
From: Jamie Zawinski <jwz@lucid.com>
Sender: jwz%thalidomide@lucid.com
To: queinnec%mailhost.cenatls.cena.dgac.fr@lucid.com (Philippe Queinnec)
