>
> How does one make Lucid (v. 19.2) display 8-bits characters as a character
> and not as an oktal value?

(setq-default ctl-arrow 'any-value-other-than-t-or-nil)

Also see the code in .../lisp/x11/x-compose.el.

	-- Jamie

