Environment:
	DECstation 5000/200
	Ultrix 4.2
	MWM
	lucid emacs 19.2 built with USE_LUCID for menu support.

Current xmodmap:

xmodmap -e "remove lock = Caps_Lock" 
	-e "add shift = Caps_Lock" 
	-e "keysym comma = comma less"
	-e "keysym period = period greater"
	-e "keycode 0xb1 = Alt_L Meta_L"

