From: carney@rocky.rational.com (Mike Carney)
Subject: font-lock and pending-del
Message-Id: <CARNEY.92Oct16094658@rocky.rational.com>
Organization: Rational, Santa Clara, CA
Distribution: alt
Date: Fri, 16 Oct 1992 17:46:58 GMT
